                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Are Friends Delight or Pain?</l>
                    <l>Could Bounty but remain</l>
                    <l>Riches were good --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>But if they only stay</l>
                    <l><app type="revision"><lem>Bolder</lem><rdg>Bolder</rdg></app>
Ampler to fly away</l>
                    <l>Riches are sad.</l>
                </lg>
